   <br> <button class="btn btn-primary btn-lg"> <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" href="https://downloads.nwtime.org/ntp/">Download NTP <img src="https://www.ntp.org/images/icons/download.svg"></a> </button> <button class="btn btn-primary btn-lg"> <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" href="https://www.ntp.org/bugs/">Report a Bug <img src="https://www.ntp.org/images/icons/bug.svg"></a> </button> 
